==English==
===Etymology===
From [[Greek]] [[δραματικός]] (''dramatikos'') "of or related to drama", from [[Ancient Greek]] [[δράμα]], ([[drama]]).

===Adjective===
'''dramatic'''
# of or relating to the [[drama]]
# striking in [[appearance]] or [[effect]]
# having a [[powerful]], [[expressive]] [[singing]] voice

====Related terms====
*[[drama]]

